                                    span#narrate-5-types  
                                        span is often used in grandparent scams. Scammers pretend to be the grandchildren and claim to be injured or tested positive for alcohol while driving, making the situation seem urgent and severe. Other types of accidents: being arrested/kidnapped when traveling overseas, legal troubles, medical emergencies
                                    //- a(href='https://www.justice.gov/criminal/criminal-fraud/identity-theft/identity-theft-and-identity-fraud.' target='_blank')
