                                    span#narrate-2-types-2  
                                        span Based on the story they use, they may ask for money for one or more of the following reasons: posting bail, paying a ransom, covering medical treatment, or funding car repairs. These reasons can easily cause 
                                    strong#narrate-3-types-2  
                                        span pressure and panic 
                                    span#narrate-4-types-2  
